cmput301.textbookhub.Models

Class OfflineCommandList

  • java.lang.Object
    • cmput301.textbookhub.Models.OfflineCommandList

  • public class OfflineCommandList
extends java.lang.Object
    OfflineCommandList is used to handle offline behaviour.

    The commands are added to a queue to be executed when the user regains internet connection.

    Since:
    2016/03/30
    See Also:
    OfflineHelper, Created by Fred on 2016/3/30.
